{"tid":2084653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"和華為等外企競爭！傳日本政府將資助通訊業700億日圓","createTime":"2020-06-29T11:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T11:52:11.000Z","uid":75656,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29292cc4cc81947cbfe95c25a8d8b577801384b3","tid":2084653,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"《日本經濟新聞》今（29）報導，有消息人士透露，日本政府將以700億日圓的規模，支持日本富士通、NEC、樂天Mobile等國內通訊產品製造商和電信商，以促進5G和「後5G」技術發展，並提高日本公司的國際競爭力，以和技術相對先進的海外公司如華為競爭。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，日本政府將動用部分經產省轄下「新能源產業技術綜合開發機構」（NEDO）、達1100億日圓的資金，支持企業開發核心網路和建立基地台。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，日本政府大筆投資國內通訊企業的目的，除了希望提升日企競爭力外，也希望能降低因進口技術造成的資訊洩漏風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3212180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3212180&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=ec8bf115\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3212180&h=304fc737\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3212180</a>"},{"pid":"defa3aa28d3924898b7effa6ca68f40e4f6c10bc","tid":2084653,"uid":5477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWsavmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWsavmb.jpg&h=cd1318a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMZoGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMZoGd.jpg&h=a6ae71e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1GZoGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1GZoGe.jpg&h=0d4591f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z00joGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz00joGf.jpg&h=4056509e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yv6Og1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F